Quest:A Taste of Honey

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Norwegian Wood
Note: Level 48 is needed to start this quest.
Note: In order to complete this quest, Wizards must be in the School of Life.

Given By: Moolinda Wu

Giver Location: Ravenwood
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Go to Shoshun Village Pond
Talk to Moolinda Wu in the School of Life
Hand In: Moolinda Wu

Reward:

400
4,200
Forest Lord
Sylvan Satyr

Leads to:

Summer is Coming (at level 58)
Ready to Hatch (at level 58)

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to A Taste of Honey should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to A Taste of Honey in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
